dict.string: This basket looks fresh out of pets. Do you happen to have any for me?
I may mew incessantly if you don't pet me. That's just part of being a kitten.
This is cat for "I'm going to take a nap while you rub my belly." You may begin.
I may be a kitten, but I know what free kibble is. Why don't you pet me?
I refuse to leave this box until you give me a sufficient number of pets.
You know, you being here and all, it seems like the perfect opportunity for you to pet me. Cats from all over will thank you.
You could just stand there and watch me be so cute, but wouldn't you rather pet me? There's free kibble involved if you do.
My name is Clover because I like them so. My middle name is Belly-pets.
Hey you! Pet me! My kitty friends need kibble!
If you think I don't want you to pet me, then you are gravely mistaken.
How have you gone this long without petting me? Kitties are in need of kibble!
What's the best way to get free kibble for cats in need, you ask? Why petting my belly, of course!
Arrr! Ahoy thar! Pet me to git my kitty hearties some free kibble. Don't be shy now!
My superpowers include feeding hungry cats every time someone pets me – go ahead and find out for yourself!
I brought you a present, now won’t you pet me and help feed hungry kitties?
How did you find me hiding back here? Well, you might as well pet me and give free kibble to my hungry feline friends.
I seem to be stuck… on helping feed hungry cats. And you can help, too! Just pet me for free kibble.
What’s that way off in the distance? Why, it’s a hungry kitty. You can help feed him just by petting me.
Gotta love these baby blues. Pet me to help other cats everywhere!
If we ruled the world, all cats would have love and kibbles. Pet me to help others!
What's that? You want to give free kibbles? Pet me to make it happen!
Look into my eyes. You will pet kitties and give kibbles to cats in need.
This smile is for you. When you pet me, kibbles go to kitties like me. Everybody wins!
Just lounging around waiting for you to rub my belly for kibbles!
We're the best of buddies and make sure to look out for each other. Take a cue from us and give us a pet so you can give kibble to kitties in need!
Come on, how can you resist this face?! If you rub my belly, I'll make sure to get free kibble to my kitty friends!
I've been google searching free kibble and I learned that all I needed was a pet from you!
Spring has sprung and by petting me you'll provide free kibble to all those kitties in need!
I'm not one of those complicated, mixed-up cats. I'm not looking for the secret to life... just kibbles and love.
It doesn't get cuter than this. Admit it - you want to pet me almost as much as you want to feed kitties in need!
Got kibbles? Haha - that's okay! Pet me now to give kibbles to handsome kitties in need - just like me.
Give a cat the right kibble, and she can conquer the world. Go on; pet me and you'll see!
I am handsome - hear me purr! Pet me to give kibbles to other kitties in need.
I don't mind living in a dog's world, as long as I can be a cat in it. I'm beautiful - pet me to give kibbles!
I promise I've been good, just one pet for kibble pretty please for me and my kitty friends!
Who me? You want to pet me?! Please do to give free kibble to me and my feline friends!
Look into my eyes and tell me you don't want to cuddle this cute face! I know you can't help but pet me for free kibble!
You're driving me crazy! Please rub my chin and you'll give me and my fluffy friends free kibble!
I'm hypnotizing you with my eyes - now pet me and help other kitties like me!
I'm just a kitten, standing in front of a human, asking them to pet her - to give free kibble to other kitties!
Who can resist these eyes? You know you want to pet to give kibble!
Relaxing in the sun, petting the perfect dog, giving free kibbles... what could be better?
You were looking for adorbs?! Here I am! Pet me and we'll help other puppies!
You cannot resist the puppy dog eyes. Pet me and give kibble. All puppies thank you.
Just look at these beautiful brown eyes. They don't call me Cuddles for nothing!
I've got my doctorate in cuteness with a specialization in adorable grins. Pet me to help other pups!
Being this cute can be pretty exhausting. Let's relax together and help feed hungry puppies in the proessess. That's what I call a win-win.
I'm too cute to resist so why even try? Pet me and help feed other puppies.
My lovely brown highlights make me adorable, and I'm not afraid to admit it. Let's team up to help other puppies, okay?
Help other puppies for free just by petting me, you say? I'm all ears!
Why am I named after I cat? I don't know.
I'm as sweet as my namesake implies. Pet me and together we can give treats to pups in need.
All this work is making me tired. Let's take a cuddle break and feed some of my canine companions in the process.
Oh hello dahling. Petting me to give free kibble to puppies in need is très chic.
I may be tired from playing, but I always have time for extra cuddles.
She's a pup with a positive outlook that's always ready to play and cuddle!
Love and loyalty in equal measure.
Giving free kibble by petting me is serious business. Let's get to work!
Together, we're an unbeatable team! Pet me to give kibble to pups who need some help.
This nose can sniff out kibble from miles away! Pet me to give free food to pups in need.
I heard there's some puppies who need kibble. Pet me to help them out!
Puppies out there are hungry? Oh no! Pet me and together we can help them!
Look at these puppy-dog eyes. Let's spend some quality time together helping pups get a good meal.
What's that you say? I get pets and puppies get a free meal? What are you waiting for?
After a long day of swimming, I'm ready for some cuddles. Pet me to help feed pups in need.
Hershey loves all kinds of treats but extra cuddles is his favorite. Pet him to help pups in need.
My energetic nature means I'm loads of fun! Pet me to help other puppies.
Spot has a goofy, fun-loving personality that shines around people. Pet him to give free food to puppies in need.
I love playing in the grass! Pet me and together we can help puppies in need.
Me? Trouble? Never! Well, maybe a little :)
I may be named after a mythological wolf, but my affection 100% real! Let's cuddle!
Personal space? Who needs that when we could cuddle instead?
Did you know that just by petting me you can help other puppies? Give it a try!
Hungry puppies getting kibble really makes my ears perk up! Pet me to help!
Look into my eyes, pet me, help other dogs - it's pretty simple really!
I'll bet you a million puppy kisses that you can help other puppies like me get kibble!
Puppies like me are hungry? That's terrible! Pet me to help!
If there's one thing I know, it's that I'm cute and you want to pet me. I guess that's two things.
My human put me in this shirt. Please pet me for kibble so I can grow out of it.
Pups like me are eating grass and flowers every day. Pet me to get them protein-rich kibble!
These eyes don't lie. I want pets and kibbles.
It looks like maybe you aren't going to pet me, but we both know that's impossible.
As you can tell, I'm not fond of the rain. It makes my fur to wet for pets!
If you can't tell, my hair could use a good russling. Care to help me out with that?
You know, even though I'm in bed that doesn't mean that I don't want pets. Hint hint, wink wink.
Is there a reason you aren't petting me? I can't think of a good one.
I will not hesitate to pounce if you don't start petting me this instant. I don't bluff!
When I do this, it means I want attention. Would you kindly oblige?
A pet a day keeps the hunger away… Help me feed hungry pups.
With a coat like this, how can you resist?! Pet me and help feed hungry dogs.
Gee, am I glad to see you. Now you can pet me and help provide free kibble!
Right behind the ears – that’s the spot! Petting me means free kibble for hungry dogs.
I’ll give you my best puppy dog eyes if you’ll just give me a quick pet. It’ll help feed other adorable pups.
Look at this teddy-bear face. You can't NOT pet me, can you? Come on, help feed other rescued cuties!
Go on, pet me. You know you want to. We'll give free kibble to other rescued pups!
Pet me and we'll give kibble to dogs in need. Go on, give it a try - I double-dog dare you!
Who can say no to this sweet smile? Let's give some food to dogs in need. Pet me - you know you want to!
Surprise! It's cuteness incarnate. Pet me, and we'll make a difference in the lives of rescued pups!
Wanna play? Okay. Here's the deal. You pet me, and we'll give food to dogs in need. One, two, three - go!
Don't leave me out in the cold; pet me! You know you want to scratch these ears and give free food!
So you wanna give some free kibbles to dogs in need? Pet me because I'm irresistible, and let's do some good.
Are you excited? I'm excited! Pet me and give free food to rescued pups like me!
Life's tough without kibble. You can change that for rescued dogs. Just pet me, and you'll see.
I'll be honest - I just want you to pet these puppy ears. Go for it. We'll give free food to rescued dogs!
Phew - playing in the California sun is hard work. Break time! Come pet me and help give food to other rescued pups.
Did you say kibble? Yes? Pet me to give free food to fun rescue dogs - just like me!
I'm the perfect pooch for petting! Go for it - and help shelter dogs like me. You'll give free kibble!
Treats for the sweet - and aren't I just sweet? Come on. Give me attention, and we'll give pups kibble!
